descriptionHtml:
Ever feel like Whiterun is a piece of S***? Well, to correct that I've taken the liberty of adding some trees to Whiterun. Thats it. It gives Whiterun a way better feel. It's way less barren and feels like a nice place.

 I have also made an Open Cities compatibility version. If you use Open cities, you'll need the OC version or [u][b][i]IT WILL NOT WORK[/i][/b][/u]
